{
  "stem": "23572.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They had the army trucks, all part of the British army, with the Magen David on the side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they were truck drivers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's-- It wasn't right for the British to drive trucks, so they gave it to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, thank God they did that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, we got all the-- all the gasoline for free.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, they used to go to-- used to go into the petrol points, which we called the-- the British army calls the-- the gasoline stations, and we used to fill up.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used to say, King George is paying for all this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to take them up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my job was to go up in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the other side of Austria was another group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to send these-- these people over the mountains to the Italian side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I used to make sure received them, put them on these-- on these army trucks, which were all manned by-- by Palestinians, Jewish Palestinians.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm not using the word Israeli, because there was no Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, we used to take them to the first railroad station, and eventually take them by train to Milan, where another group took over.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, my job was, first of all, to talk to the Italian police.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So each train has Italian police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Explain to them all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These are relatives of British military personnel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I used to give them cigarettes, and-- and we had wine, and everything else.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know, I used to tell them we're taking these-- these people over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're taking them to Milan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No problem.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They're no smugglers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I would do it-- I would do this trip maybe three times a week.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Three times a week.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
